data.description: Nestled in the serene coastal surroundings at Coral Reef, this 2-bedroom, 2-bath cottage is the epitome of charm and tranquility. The outdoor area includes a spacious covered deck with water views to Estes Flats.  Making it perfect for morning coffee or evening sunsets. This home offers plenty of space for boat parking and a storage room that could be turned into a bar area like some of your neighbors, or just use it as a storage room. This home features a well-equipped kitchen with stainless steel appliances and a breakfast bar with an open concept living area with water views. You will enjoy the use of the community pool and boat washing bay.  Tucked away in a quiet neighborhood, this cottage provides the serenity coastal living while still being within easy reach of local amenities and the proximity to sandy beaches, restaurants, marinas, shopping and the best fishing in South Texas.  Call now to view this cute home.
